"{\"uid\": \"bernews.com-2024-07-bermuda-olympic-schedule-sunday-july-28\", \"text\": \"Bermuda has two athletes in action tomorrow [Sunday July 28] with rower Dara Alizadeh scheduled to compete for his second day and swimmer Jack Harvey set to make his Olympic debut, where he will compete in the 100m backstroke.        Bernews will be providing comprehensive coverage of Bermuda's athletes in the coming weeks, thanks to our sponsors Butterfield & Vallis, Auto Solutions, Clarien Bank and One Communications.  #2024Olympics#Bermuda2024#Olympics  Category:All,Sports  .  Archives:  Categories:  Tags:  Bernews\"}"